**ShrI subrahmaNya prasanna mAlA mantram**  <br><br>

https://sanskritdocuments.org/doc_subrahmanya/subrahmaNyaprasannamAlAmantram.itx

OM asya shrIsubrahmaNyaprasannamAlAmantram |
OM namo bhagavate rudrakumArAya, ShaDAnanAya,
shaktihastAya, aShTAdasha lochanAya, shikhAmaNi
prala~NkR^itAya, krau~nchagirimardanAya, tArakAsuramAraNAya,
OM\-shrIM\-aiM\-klIM\-hrIM\-huM\-phaT\- svAhA || 1||

OM namo bhagavate gaurIsutAya, aghorarUpAya,
ugrarUpAya, AkAshasvarUpAya, sharavaNabhavAya, shaktishUla\-
gadAparashuhastAya, pAshA~Nkusha\-tomara\-bANa\-musaladharAya,
aneka shastrAla~NkR^itAya, OM shrI subrahmaNyAya,
hAra\-nUpura\-keyUra\-kanaka\-kuNDala\-mekhalAtyaneka
sarvAbharaNAla~NkR^itAya, sadAnanda sharIrAya, sakala
rudragaNasevitAya, sarva lokavasha~NkarAya, sakala
bhUtagaNa sevitAya, OM\-raM\-naM\-laM skandarUpAya,
sakala mantragaNa sevitAya, ga~NgAputrAya,
shAkinI\-DAkinI\-bhUta\-preta\-pishAchagaNasevitAya,
asurakula nAshanAya, OM\-shrIM\-aiM\-klIM\-hrIM\-huM\-phaT svAhA || 2||

OM namo bhagavate tejorUpAya, bhUtagraha, pretagraha,
pishAchagraha, yakShagraha, rAkShasagraha, vetAlagraha,
bhairavagraha, asuragraha, sarvagrahAn AkarShaya
AkarShaya, bandhaya bandhaya, santrAsaya santrAsaya,
ArpATaya ArpATaya, Chedaya Chedaya, shoShaya shoShaya,
balena prahAraya prahAraya, sarvagrahAn mAraya mAraya,
OM shrIM\-klIM\-hrIM paramantra, paratantra, parayantra,
paravidyA bandhanAya, Atma mantra, Atma tantra,
Atma vidyA prakaTanAya, para vidyAchChedanAya,
AtmavidyA sthApanAya, OM\-shrIM\-klIM\-hrIM\-huM\-phaT svAhA || 3||

OM namo bhagavate mahAbalaparAkramAya mAM rakSha rakSha,
OM Aveshaya Aveshaya, OM sharavaNabhavAya, OM\-shrIM\-klIM\-
sauH aiM sarvagrahAn mama vashIkaraNa kuru kuru, sarvagrahaM
Chindi Chindi, sarvagrahaM mohaya mohaya, AkarShaya
AkarShaya, Aveshaya Aveshaya, uchchATaya uchchATaya,
sarvagrahAn mama vashIkaraNa kuru kuru, OM\-sauH raM\-laM\-
ekAhnika, dvayAhnika, trayAhnika, chAturthika,
pa~nchamajvara, ShaShThamajvara, saptamajvara, aShTamajvara,
navamajvara, mahAviShamajvara, sannipAdajvara, brahmajvara,
viShNujvara, yakShajvara, sakalajvara, hataM kuru kuru |
samastajvaraM uchchATaya uchchATaya, bhedena prahAraya prahAraya,
OM\-shrIM\-klIM\-hrIM\-huM\-phaT\-svAhA || 4||

OM namo bhagavate dvAdasha bhujAya, takShakAnanda
kArkoTaka sa~Ngha mahAsa~Ngha\-padma\-mahApadma\-vAsuki\-
gulika\-mahAgulikAdIn samastaviShaM nAshaya nAshaya,
uchchATaya uchchATaya, rAjavashyaM \- bhUtavashyaM \- astravashyaM \-
puruShavashyaM \- mR^igasarpa vashyaM \- sarva vashIkaraNa kuru kuru |
japena mAM rakSha rakSha, OM sharavaNabhava, OM shrIM\-klIM
vashIkaraNa kuru kuru, OM sharavaNabhava OM \- aiM AkarShaya
AkarShaya, OM sharavaNabhava OM stambhaya stambhaya, OM
sharavaNabhava  OM sammohaya sammohaya, OM sharavaNabhava
OM \- raM mAraya mAraya, OM sharavaNabhava OM\-aiM\-laM
uchchATaya uchchATaya, OM sharavaNabhava OM \- shrIM
vidveshaya vidveshaya, vAta\-pitta shleShmA.a.adi vyAdhIn
nAshaya nAshaya, sarva shatrUn hana hana, sarva duShTAn
santrAsaya, santrAsaya, mama sAdhUn pAlaya pAlaya, mAM
rakSha rakSha, agnimukhaM \- jalamukhaM \- bANamukhaM \-
siMhamukhaM \- vyAghramukhaM \- sarpamukhaM \- senAmukhaM
stambhaya stambhaya, bandhaya bandhaya, shoShaya shoShaya,
mohaya mohaya, shrImbalaM Chedaya Chedaya, bandhaya bandhaya
japena prahAraya prahAraya, OM\-shrIM\-klIM\-hrIM\-huM\-huM\-phaT svAhA || 5||

OM namo bhagavate mahAbala parAkramAya, kAlabhairava \-
kapAlabhairava \- krodhabhairava \- uddaNDa bhairava \- mArtANDa bhairava\-
saMhArabhairava \- samasta bhairavAn uchchATaya uchchATaya,
bandhaya bandhaya, japena prahAraya prahAraya, OM \- shrIM troTaya
troTaya, OM \- naM dIpaya dIpaya, OM \- IM santApaya santApaya,
OM shrIM unmattaya unmattaya, OM\-shrIM\-hrIM\-klIM\-aiM\-IM\-laM\-sauH
pAshupatAstra, nArAyaNAstra, subrahmaNyAstra, indrAstra,
AgneyAstra, brahmAstra, yamayAstra, vAruNAstra, vAyuvyAstra,
kuberAstra, IshAnAstra, andhakArAstra, gandharvAstra, asurAstra,
garuDAstra, sarpAstra, parvatAstra, ashvAstra, gajAstra, siMhAstra,
mohanAstra, bhairavAstra, mAyAstra, sarvAstrAn nAshaya nAshaya,
bhakShaya bhakShaya, uchchATaya uchchATaya, OM shrIM\-klIM\-hrIM chidraroga,
shvetaroga, kuShTaroga, apasmAraroga, bhakSharoga, bahumUtraroga,
premega, granthiroga, mahodara, raktakShaya, sarvaroga, shveta, kuShTa,
pANDuroga, ati sarvaroga, mUtrakR^isna, gulmaroga, sarvarogAn hana hana,
uchchATaya uchchATaya, sarvarogAn nAshaya nAshaya,
OM\-laM\-sauH huM\-phaT svAhA || 6||

makShikA\-mashakA\-madgagusha\-pipIlikA\-mUShikA\-mArjAlA\-shyena\-kR^itra\-vAyasa
duShTa pakShi doShAn nAshaya nAshaya | duShTa jantUn nAshaya nAshaya,
OM shrIM\-aiM\-klIM\-hrIM\-IM\-naM\-laM\-sauH sharavaNabhava huM phaT svAhA ||

iti shrImat kumAratantre hayagrIvaagastyasaMvAde
shatamiti paTalaM nAma  OM shrI subrahmaNya prasanna mAlAmantraM sampUrNam |

